@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Producer Flow

participant Producer
participant KafkaClient
participant KafkaBroker
participant Topic

Producer -> KafkaClient: Create Producer Instance
Producer -> KafkaClient: Connect to Broker
KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Establish Connection
KafkaBroker --> KafkaClient: Connection Acknowledged

loop For each message
    Producer -> KafkaClient: Send Message
    KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Produce Message to Topic
    KafkaBroker -> Topic: Store Message
    Topic --> KafkaBroker: Acknowledge
    KafkaBroker --> KafkaClient: Send Success
    KafkaClient --> Producer: Message Sent
end

Producer -> KafkaClient: Disconnect
KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Close Connection

@enduml

